values:
I want to make you scream!
I want to make you moan!
I want to make you make you make you.
Listening to "Let's Go Crazy" makes me want to cry!

If you loved him, tell him you hate him.
If you loved him, tell him you loath him.

You owe him that much.
You owe him the truth.
Drop your pathetic ruse.

Seeing how long I can go without electronics, completely.
Starting now.
I think I'm in love with a lark that made a mess out of my bed.
Why are you smiling in all those pictures?
